              "content": "GLASS TREATMENT: background-blur 12px, fill gradient #1A1816EB → #13120FE0 (linear, 180deg). Border: gradient stroke #3D3A3580 → #1E1C19 (1px, inside). Connector line: #353530 0.5px. Card floats 32px right of node center. Dismiss: opacity 0 → 1 over 150ms, reverse on leave.",
