              "content": "STATE PRIORITY (highest wins): Streaming > Selected > Hover > Active > Dimmed > Rest\n\nRARITY SUPPRESSION: Selected and Streaming suppress orbital arcs + particles (they share r+5 to r+14 zone). Aura (Tier 3+, r*2.2) persists — it occupies a larger radius. Body fill, core dot, and labels always persist regardless of state.",
