                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 700,
                  "content": "Progressive disclosure session switcher. Six states from collapsed pill to full session manager with search. Glass treatment, #DD0000 streaming indicator, Inconsolata metadata. Status dots: #808080 idle, #DD0000 active — no green. State 6 adds natural-language search. 'Clip to Session' in Full Open creates new session from clipped subgraph.",
