                  "content": "Three layers of shortcut discovery:\n\n1. CONTEXTUAL HINTS — When hovering a tool button (e.g., canvas tools branch icon), a tooltip shows the shortcut key alongside the action name: ‘Branch (B)’\n\n2. FIRST-RUN — On first session, the shortcuts overlay auto-shows for 5s with a ‘Got it’ dismiss button. Does not reappear.\n\n3. ON DEMAND — Cmd+/ or ‘?’ key opens the full overlay at any time. The overlay appears with glass-elevated treatment and dismisses on Escape or click-away.\n\n4. INLINE BADGES — Context menu items show shortcut hints at right edge (already present in Section 1).",
                  "lineHeight": 1.8,
                  "fontFamily": "Inconsolata",
                  "fontSize": 10
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
