                              "name": "msg4txt",
                              "fill": "#C8C8C8",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "Specificity wins. Component-level tokens override semantic tokens, which override primitives. When two systems collide at the same level, the last-applied source wins — configurable via priority weights.",
